Author/Contributors:
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
- Kevin Meinert <kevin@vrsource.org>
- Patrick Hartlong <patrick@vrac.iastate.edu>

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
Description:
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
This is a very simple build system.  It uses GNU-Make to build and some common 
UNIX commands to detect platform.  For simple projects, this utility can 
build cross platform SO, static LIB, and EXE resources...


For a more complex projects, check out Doozer++ (at sourceforge) by 
Patrick Hartling.

